author: Warhammer
description:
Blood Claws are the impetuous Upstarts of the Space Wolves Legion, today Jake will show you how to paint one up and make a fancy ice base to go alongside it!
Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

Contrast:
Pylar Glacier
Talasar Blue
Gryph Hound Orange

Base:
Averland Sunset
Balthasar Gold 
Barak Nar Burgundy 
Corax White 
Leadbealcher 
Mechanicus Standard Grey 
Mephiston Red
Retributor Armour
Zandri Dust 


Layer:
Blue Horror 
Dark Reaper 
Evil Suns Scarlett 
Fenrisian Grey
Russ Grey
White Scar

Shade:
Agrax earthshade 

Technical:
Contrast Medium

Brushes:
M layer
M shade
s dry 
If you're new to painting, our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started.
